description: Ms. Cheezious, the sexiest new food truck in Miami, rolls out your favorite comfort food - grilled cheese sandwiches like mom used to make, only not quite as innocent as mom used to make!Not only will you indulge in classic melt-in-your-mouth grilled cheese, but Ms. Cheezious will also arouse your palette with signature specialties like the Crabby Cheese Melt. Get turned on by the many selections available to create your own mind-blowing sandwich. Did we mention your mouth will water? Dip your favorite grilled cheese in a side of brown gravy, or have it with a steamy bowl of savory tomato soup. Menu items include hot, grilled sandwiches, soups, chili, and fries; take your pick, Ms. Cheezious promises to keep you coming back for more.Be on the look out for the hottest sandwich lady in Miami. Come experience her full-bodied flavors. Ms. Cheezious brings the party to your mouth!
name: Ms. Cheezious
